components.name: Check PCD SFTP Folder
components.description: Runs a Kubernetes job that verifies the availability and contents of the SFTP folder before the ETL starts. Uses the job template defined in the Airflow variable `pcd_emtysftp_job`.

upstream_policy.description: First task in the pipeline, no upstream dependencies.

components.name: Check PCD Shared Folder
components.description: Runs a Kubernetes job that validates accessibility of the shared folder after the SFTP check. Uses the job template defined in the Airflow variable `pcd_emtydir_job`.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful SFTP folder validation.

components.name: Extract PCD API Data
components.description: Executes HTTP POST requests to 18 different PCDrelated endpoints in parallel, validating that each response returns HTTP 200 and returning the JSON payloads.

upstream_policy.description: Triggered after the shared folder validation completes.

connections.purpose: call the various PCD HTTP endpoints

components.name: Process and Load PCD Data
components.description: Runs the main ETL Kubernetes job that processes all API response data and uploads the resulting PCD dataset to its destination. Uses the job template defined in the Airflow variable `pcd_job`.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after all parallel API extraction tasks finish successfully.

components.name: ETL Notification
components.description: Sends email notifications after the pipeline finishes, reporting success or failure and including details of any failed tasks. Executes regardless of upstream outcome (trigger rule `all_done`).

upstream_policy.description: Runs after all upstream tasks complete, regardless of success or failure.
